<h2>2. Tulips</h2>

<p>Tulips are wonderful. There are so many different types and colours; reds, yellows, oranges, the rarer purples, both block colours and stripey. One of my favourites is red with white frilly ends, called a Tulip New Santa, which I think is amazing. They’re another flower that brings the mood of Spring. You can often find them in parks and gardens, and like daffodils, can often be bought in supermarkets around February and March.</p>

