<h2>4. Lily of the valley</h2>

<p>Lily of the valley is a plant that’s new to me. I was aware of it when it came to fragrances that my grandmother liked, but not much more. However, since starting my wildlife watching I’ve started to look out for them more.</p>

<p>They look like large white bluebells, but with rounder bells and larger leaver. I’ve only seen them outside of cities, so they might not be hugely easy to find. But if you do, they are very charming, and you can see why it can be some people’s favourite flower.</p>

